author: Ben Gittleson
title: As Trump pushes economic reopening, health risks and key questions unanswered
description: The guidelines, like those President Donald Trump has issued before, will likely serve only as recommendations to governors who have been calling the shots.
content: As President Donald Trump teased an announcement Thursday of how some states could start to "reopen" amid the novel coronavirus pandemic, key questions remained about the health and economic risks involved, how willing Americans would be to head back to work … [+5465 chars]
